{"tid":596152,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(JJ插求教) HDD死左 想順便升級女","createTime":"2018-03-17T10:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T06:37:36.000Z","uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0ad9403c68f4d2ec6834862187101753366ea2","tid":596152,"uid":134589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"部機用左4年 HDD最先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想順便升級下條女<br />\n但在下實在唔知D硬件岩用定唔岩用 火牛sup唔support到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想問下咁多位清<br />\n<br />\nList 如下:<br />\n<br />\nCPU: Intel Core i7-4770<br />\n<br />\n老母板: MSI B85M-E45<br />\n<br />\nRam: Kingston 8GB DDR3-1600<br />\n<br />\nSSD: Plextor M5 Pro Series 128GB<br />\n<br />\nHDD: Seagate 1TB ST1000DM003 (7200rpm, SATA3) &lt;---死鳩左<br />\n<br />\nDisplay Card: Leadtek Quadro K2000 2GB<br />\n<br />\n牛: Corsair CX600v3 600 Watts (80 plus)<br />\n<br />\nCase: NZXT 410<br />\n<br />\n想加ram 加ssd 換卡 換HDD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時都係打LOL 睇戲<br />\n出黎做野之後都好少用部電腦rend圖 所以想換埋張卡<br />\n<br />\n謝巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 有冇巴打知邊到整HDD抵玩"},{"pid":"81021837159bf963da4cecabd1a97829c432c610","tid":596152,"uid":134589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"屌標題出少左幾隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(JJ插<span style=\"color: re